Our journey hasn‚Äôt been an easy one, we‚Äôve faced so many obstacles as individuals but also as a family. My dad and I haven‚Äôt had the easiest of relationships. He worked so hard to create an opportunity for us as a family and because of him I am where I am today. In the search for success, with all the pressure it put on us all, we were so immersed in the drive to succeed that we that we lost sight of what was most important, our relationship. Over time, we lost that father son bond and it has been something we have both wanted back for so long. the past couple years we‚Äôve been growing closer and this winter break I asked my dad to come visit me so we could spend some time together, just us. We hadn‚Äôt done this before so to finally get to spend quality time with him has brought me so much happiness. I just wanted to share this with you. Family is the most important thing in the world. You can‚Äôt chose your family but you can make it work with them no matter your differences, they are the ones that will be there when you have nothing. Sending everyone positivity and love. #hamilton #fatherandson #grateful
